# Silk & Olive Restaurant Web Application

Silk & Olive is a modern web application designed for a gourmet restaurant. It showcases a digital menu, allows users to view details of menu items, manage a shopping cart, and provides contact and booking information.

## Setup Instructions

To get the application running locally on your machine, follow these steps:

1. **Clone the Repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name.git
   cd your-repo-name

2. **Navigate to the project directory:**
   ```bash
   cd your-repository-name

3. **Install dependencies:**
   ```bash
   npm install

If you have any environment variables or configurations, set them up as required.

## Functionality Description
Home Page: Displays an attractive hero section with a carousel showcasing different dishes.
Menu View: Users can browse through a list of menu items, each item showing a picture, name, and price.
Item Detail View: Clicking on a menu item navigates to a detailed view, showing more information such as ingredients and a larger image.
Cart Functionality: Users can add items to a cart, view their cart, and adjust quantities or remove items.
